{
  "stem": "17625.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he slept there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The night shift slept and the day shift slept.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But at that-- at the time when the fire was there, there was a fire in, in Crematorium 2.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they said we need workers to, to Crematorium-- empty out mattresses, whatever there was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I heard it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, I don't want to stay here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't want to stay in the block.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I went, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and we cleaned out the, the, the-- all the burned things, whatever was.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We worked a few hours.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Going back, I found out-- I saw-- I saw my, my people going to the [POLISH], to the [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know what is the [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My cousin and all, all the-- they went to the [POLISH] and all the old ones.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What happened is when, when, when I went to work, the lagerfuhrer-- before that it was the kapo or the blockalteste.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But at that time, it was the lagerfuhrer came in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He took the charts.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He went instead of, of, of the back, he went to the front.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So he took all the old ones, you know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So they called my name, my cousin's name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He went.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And all those who came with my transport had to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They called my name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They took the next one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I came back and I was-- I-- and, and, and this was the story what happened then.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A few people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From my kommando-- from the people-- when we came for lunch there, I saw there was no way-- there was no way-- they-- it, it, it-- waiting for the dead.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If they threw grenades, if somebody went to a hole, you took a grenade.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
